Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 70ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1
Set WindowBar Rings
Set BorderRadius 8
Set Framerate 30

Hide
Type "PS1='\033[32m\033[1m~/projects/myapp\033[0m \033[90m$\033[0m '" Enter
Type "alias gru='/tmp/gru-demo-script.sh'" Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show

Sleep 800ms
Type "gru do 47"
Sleep 600ms
Enter
Sleep 17s
